article.headline: Jackson scores 16 as Charlotte downs Utah Valley 62-45

images.name: Utah Valley Wolverines vs. Charlotte 49ers: Full Highlights
images.caption: Utah Valley Wolverines vs. Charlotte 49ers: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Jackson scores 16 as Charlotte downs Utah Valley 62-45
article.story: CHARLOTTE, N.C. -- — Dishon Jackson had 16 points in Charlotte's 62-45 win over Utah Valley on Wednesday night. Jackson added seven rebounds for the 49ers (2-1). Igor Milicic Jr. scored 15 points while shooting 5 for 9, including 3 for 6 from beyond the arc, and added 12 rebounds. Lu'Cye Patterson had 13 points and was 5 of 12 shooting, including 0 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 5 from the line. Drake Allen led the Wolverines (2-1) in scoring, finishing with 12 points, six rebounds and two steals. Utah Valley also got 10 points from Caleb Stone-Carrawell. In addition, Trevin Dorius finished with eight points and eight rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
